{
  "stem": "1721.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I was told that I spoke to Czech years later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't recall it, and I obviously forgot a lot of-- I obviously don't recall any of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So but I remember being on-- coming into Ellis Island, unloading and going through the sitting, and going through the processing, and you know, stamping us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Suitcase.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I think we landed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think they gave us, each person $14 or $15.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took us and they allowed us-- I think the HIAS had a-- had a building that we could stay in for a few days until we found a place to live.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they obviously didn't want to dump us on the docks and say you're on your own.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were able to get us to some place down the lower east side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like an apartment building that they had taken over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would-- the HIAS group would allow the immigrants to stay there for whatever time it took us to find an apartment.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And usually they encouraged us to do it very quickly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I don't think we were there for days, maybe a week or so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I did-- and I spoke no English-- but I did recall one day I was-- I mean, obviously there was no school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was in August.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "School was not in session.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember sort of wandering around the street, and somebody comes up to me and said, do you want to go to a summer camp?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't understand what the English was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But anyway, it was translated for me, and I said sure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother said fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It turned out to be Eddie Cantor's Surprise Lake Camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
